Name: X air combat
About the game: Immerse yourself in an epic aerial battle with hundreds of enemies. The background of the story takes place on an island in the Pacific. Players need to fly an aircraft carrier to protect their allies. The main goal-destroy as many enemy aircraft as possible. Game features: Real third-person driving experience Fast-paced aerial combat Soar into the sky, bomb the enemy, shoot the enemy aircraft, and look forward to your path to the ace pilot!
